title: The Hood Collection complete, Holyoke Golden Age
description:
This is a complete compiled collection!!!


Golden Age Origin Edit
FBI Agent Craig Williams, frustrated by criminals who escape the law and operate outside the FBI's jurisdiction,  puts on a costume and fights crime although he has no super powers.

His enemies included the Death's Head, the Red Lash, Voris, The Fire Eater, and the Vulture's Claw.

Golden Age Appearances  Edit
Cat-Man Comics #5-26, 29
Veri Best Sure Fire Comics #1 (Cover Only)
